7
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,079
Dongfang Xi.

8
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,280
Have you found me?

9
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:01,759
Of course.

10
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:06,480
