15
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,200
or I die.

16
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:15,799
Am I right?

17
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,159
Yes.

18
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,239
There's no third outcome.

19
00:01:38,159 --> 00:01:39,200
This is

20
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,959
my first time seeing you here.

21
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:42,680
It really is you.

22
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:47,079
I was being selfish
to have made the bet with you.

23
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,400
When I was the novel's male lead,
Dongfang Yan,

24
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,200
everything I did

25
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:55,000
was the outcome
of precise calculations.

26
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:56,760
Yet facing you,

27
00:01:57,079 --> 00:01:58,200
I always wanted

28
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,400
to approach you as my true self.

29
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,000
I'm sorry.

30
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:06,159
I used the bet
to trick you into being with me.

31
00:02:20,287 --> 00:02:22,687
(Nobody can boss you around.)

32
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,360
(You've always been
like this since young.)

33
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,800
From now on,
you're not allowed to show up

34
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,080
wherever Xi is.

35
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:38,400
Do you know who I am?

36
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,560
(The villainess, Dongfang Xi.)

37
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:43,680
(Back in school, she bullied classmates
in the name of her family.)

38
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,479
I was wrong, Ms. Dongfang.

39
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:45,560
I won't do that again!

40
00:02:45,759 --> 00:02:47,280
This isn't the first time
you've been caught

41
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,879
secretly filming
in the girls' locker room, no?

42
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,800
Since you can't control yourself...

43
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,960
I'll send someone over
to teach you a lesson.

44
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,319
By the way,

45
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:02,199
your family's cooperation
with Dongfang Group

46
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:04,080
is over.

47
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,879
I was wrong, Ms. Dongfang!

48
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:09,439
Please spare my family!

49
00:03:11,159 --> 00:03:13,159
(That was when I realized)

50
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:15,400
(the novel only showed the surface,)

51
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:17,199
(not the whole truth.)

52
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:19,159
As for the photo scandal,

53
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:21,199
you, who leaked the pictures,

54
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:23,000
should be ashamed.

55
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:25,800
System.

56
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,759
You can't kill me.

57
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,639
What say you, Yan?

58
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:55,240
Tell me.

59
00:03:55,599 --> 00:03:56,879
Did you do that out of responsibility?

60
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:58,879
